node.text: Went live with the @whitehouse & our Press Secretary #JenPsaki today to talk about the New Child Tax Credit! @matthew_noszka

Happy first Father’s Day to the hottest baby daddy around 🥰 @matthew_noszka …Watching you with our little munchkin makes my heart melt, but also pisses me off because I already know she’s a daddy’s girl 😩
